      </div>
      <div>
        <h3>Mon - Aug 5th</h3>
        <p>
          <b>Deadpool & Wolverine</b> - 3:40pm @ Scotiabank Theatre
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3>Tues - Aug 6th</h3>
        <p>
          <b>Go Karting</b> - 2pm @ <a href="https://www.topkarting.com/"
